   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Program for the Expansion and Improvement of Initial and Basic Education</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="ES">Programa de Ampliaci&#xF3;n y Mejoramiento de la Educaci&#xF3;n Inicial y B&#xE1;sica</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="ES">1. General. Mejorar la educaci&#xF3;n inicial y b&#xE1;sica para apoyar la formaci&#xF3;n de futuras generaciones las que, con mayor instrucci&#xF3;n, puedan ampliar el abanico de oportunidades para romper el c&#xED;rculo de pobreza y la exclusi&#xF3;n social.2. Espec&#xED;ficos. Colaborar con el proceso de ampliaci&#xF3;n de la cobertura, el mejoramiento de la calidad y el aumento de la equidad de la educaci&#xF3;n en los niveles inicial y b&#xE1;sico, focalizando su atenci&#xF3;n preferentemente en la poblaci&#xF3;n de menores ingresos. Adicionalmente se financiar&#xED;an acciones de fortalecimiento institucional del MECD, particularmente en &#xE1;reas vinculadas con el programa.</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The program will consist on the following components: (i) institutional strengthening of MED through changes in the management structure, human resources administration and management information system; (ii) improvement of coverage in initial and basic education also including the expansion to 9th grade and the establishment of a financial plan to maintenance of infraestructure; (iii) teacher training improvement through the implementation of a continous training strategy for initial and basic educ. teachers; (iv) adaptation of the curriculum to the integral and participative model that the government is supporting; and (v) monitoring and evaluation system that will allow to evaluate continously and consistently the results of the changes introduced by the MED in curriculum, teacher training and institutional management.</narrative>
  </description>
